{"TopicId":31093,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"External seats (0.20)","CreatedByName":"1of6Billion","CreatedById":46191,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-06-03T12:29:26Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"1of6Billion","CreatedById":46191,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-06-03T12:29:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ESo, How do they work?\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThey are listed as command pod, but whenever I build a contraption with these, I don\u0027t get any Kerbals to take the seat. Neither is it possible to control the rocket. What am I doing wrong?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KasperVld","CreatedById":40700,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-06-03T12:37:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThe seats are not occupied by default, so you\u0027ll also have to add another command pod or get a Kerbal from another place (eg a space station). Once you get close to the seat, rightclick it and select board \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"1of6Billion","CreatedById":46191,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-06-03T14:56:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022KasperVld\u0022 data-cite=\u0022KasperVld\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EThe seats are not occupied by default, so you\u0027ll also have to add another command pod or get a Kerbal from another place (eg a space station). Once you get close to the seat, rightclick it and select board \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAh, OK. So Nothing wrong there. Thanks \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"zanzibar196","CreatedById":67228,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-06-04T02:05:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHere is a video showing how an external seat works:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ciframe width=\u0022459\u0022 height=\u0022344\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/Spu6Shjo2Mg?feature=oembed\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\n"}]}